Name: Pew-Pew Rocket
About the game: Pew Pew Rocket is a space shooter but with a unique twist, Instead of shooting lasers and plasma's it mixes together a guitar hero type beat system in which to destroy your enemy! Instead of explosions its instead beautiful fireworks! The game features 3 difficulties to play through, 3 ships and a sick soundtrack for each level. You play by shooting out a Directional key, or X,A,Y,B on the Xbox Controller, and you will need to hit the correct key as it passes over an enemy ship. You get scored by how accurate you are for each shot so try to get those perfects as much as you can! The beautiful effects, fast, unique game play and awesome soundtrack will get you hooked!
